{
  "video_id": "JP0w9lZoLwU",
  "title": "David Merrill: Toy tiles that talk to each other",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 14160.0,
      "text": "I want to start out by asking you to think back to when you were a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14160.0,
      "end_time": 16160.0,
      "text": "playing with blocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16160.0,
      "end_time": 18160.0,
      "text": "As you figured out how to reach out and grasp,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18160.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "pick them up and move them around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "you were actually learning how to think and solve problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 25160.0,
      "text": "by understanding and manipulating spatial relationships."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25160.0,
      "end_time": 28160.0,
      "text": "Spatial reasoning is deeply connected"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "to how we understand a lot of the world around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30160.0,
      "end_time": 32159.0,
      "text": "So, as a computer scientist"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 32159.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "inspired by this utility of our interactions with physical objects --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "along with my adviser Pattie, and my collaborator Jeevan Kalanithi --"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "I started to wonder -- what if when we used a computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 45160.0,
      "text": "instead of having this one mouse cursor that was a like a digital fingertip"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45160.0,
      "end_time": 47160.0,
      "text": "moving around a flat desktop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47160.0,
      "end_time": 51160.0,
      "text": "what if we could reach in with both hands and grasp information physically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51160.0,
      "end_time": 53160.0,
      "text": "arranging it the way we wanted?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53160.0,
      "end_time": 56160.0,
      "text": "This question was so compelling that we decided to explore the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56160.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "by building Siftables."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58160.0,
      "end_time": 61160.0,
      "text": "In a nutshell, a Siftable is an interactive computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61160.0,
      "end_time": 63160.0,
      "text": "the size of a cookie."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63160.0,
      "end_time": 65160.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re able to be moved around by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65160.0,
      "end_time": 67160.0,
      "text": "they can sense each other, they can sense their motion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67160.0,
      "end_time": 70160.0,
      "text": "and they have a screen and a wireless radio."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 72160.0,
      "text": "Most importantly, they&#39;re physical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72160.0,
      "end_time": 75160.0,
      "text": "so like the blocks, you can move them just by reaching out and grasping."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75160.0,
      "end_time": 78160.0,
      "text": "And Siftables are an example of a new ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 80160.0,
      "text": "of tools for manipulating digital information."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80160.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "And as these tools become more physical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 85160.0,
      "text": "more aware of their motion, aware of each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85160.0,
      "end_time": 87160.0,
      "text": "and aware of the nuance of how we move them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87160.0,
      "end_time": 90160.0,
      "text": "we can start to explore some new and fun interaction styles."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90160.0,
      "end_time": 92160.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;m going to start with some simple examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92160.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "This Siftable is configured to show video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 97160.0,
      "text": "and if I tilt it in one direction, it&#39;ll roll the video this way;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97160.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "if I tilt it the other way it rolls it backwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 103160.0,
      "text": "And these interactive portraits are aware of each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 103160.0,
      "end_time": 106160.0,
      "text": "So if I put them next to each other, they get interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 106160.0,
      "end_time": 110160.0,
      "text": "If they get surrounded, they notice that too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 110160.0,
      "end_time": 112160.0,
      "text": "they might get a little flustered."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112160.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "And they can also sense their motion and tilt."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 121160.0,
      "text": "One of the interesting implications on interaction, we started to realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 121160.0,
      "end_time": 123160.0,
      "text": "was that we could use everyday gestures on data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123160.0,
      "end_time": 126160.0,
      "text": "like pouring a color the way we might pour a liquid."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 130160.0,
      "text": "So in this case, we&#39;ve got three Siftables configured to be paint buckets"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 130160.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "and I can use them to pour color into that central one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 135160.0,
      "text": "where they get mixed."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135160.0,
      "end_time": 138160.0,
      "text": "If we overshoot, we can pour a little bit back."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139160.0,
      "end_time": 142160.0,
      "text": "There are also some neat possibilities for education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142160.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "like language, math and logic games"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 146160.0,
      "text": "where we want to give people the ability to try things quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146160.0,
      "end_time": 149160.0,
      "text": "and view the results immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149160.0,
      "end_time": 151160.0,
      "text": "So here I&#39;m --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151160.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153160.0,
      "end_time": 157160.0,
      "text": "This is a Fibonacci sequence that I&#39;m making with a simple equation program."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 157160.0,
      "end_time": 161160.0,
      "text": "Here we have a word game that&#39;s kind of like a mash-up between Scrabble and Boggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161160.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "Basically, in every round"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 163160.0,
      "end_time": 165160.0,
      "text": "you get a randomly assigned letter on each Siftable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 165160.0,
      "end_time": 168160.0,
      "text": "and as you try to make words it checks against a dictionary."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "Then, after about 30 seconds, it reshuffles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171160.0,
      "end_time": 174160.0,
      "text": "and you have a new set of letters and new possibilities to try."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 174160.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 175160.0,
      "end_time": 176160.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 178160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178160.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "So these are some kids that came on a field trip to the Media Lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180160.0,
      "end_time": 183160.0,
      "text": "and I managed to get them to try it out, and shoot a video."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190160.0,
      "end_time": 192160.0,
      "text": "They really loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 195160.0,
      "text": "And, one of the interesting things about this kind of application"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195160.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "is that you don&#39;t have to give people many instructions."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 200160.0,
      "text": "All you have to say is, \"Make words,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 200160.0,
      "end_time": 202160.0,
      "text": "and they know exactly what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202160.0,
      "end_time": 204160.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s another few people trying it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 211160.0,
      "end_time": 214160.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s our youngest beta tester, down there on the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216160.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "Turns out, all he wanted to do was to stack the Siftables up."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222160.0,
      "end_time": 225160.0,
      "text": "So to him, they were just blocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 229160.0,
      "text": "Now, this is an interactive cartoon application."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 229160.0,
      "end_time": 234160.0,
      "text": "And we wanted to build a learning tool for language learners."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "And this is Felix, actually."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 237160.0,
      "end_time": 239160.0,
      "text": "And he can bring new characters into the scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 239160.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "just by lifting the Siftables off the table that have that character shown on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "Here, he&#39;s bringing the sun out."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 247160.0,
      "end_time": 249160.0,
      "text": "Video: The sun is rising."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 249160.0,
      "end_time": 252160.0,
      "text": "David Merrill: Now he&#39;s brought a tractor into the scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253160.0,
      "end_time": 255160.0,
      "text": "Video: The orange tractor."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 255160.0,
      "end_time": 257159.0,
      "text": "Good job! Yeah!"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 258160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "text": "DM: So by shaking the Siftables and putting them next to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "he can make the characters interact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 264160.0,
      "text": "Video: Woof!"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 264160.0,
      "end_time": 266160.0,
      "text": "DM: inventing his own narrative."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 266160.0,
      "end_time": 267160.0,
      "text": "Video: Hello!"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267160.0,
      "end_time": 269160.0,
      "text": "DM: It&#39;s an open-ended story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 271160.0,
      "text": "and he gets to decide how it unfolds."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 274160.0,
      "end_time": 276160.0,
      "text": "Video: Fly away, cat."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 285160.0,
      "text": "DM: So, the last example I have time to show you today"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285160.0,
      "end_time": 287160.0,
      "text": "is a music sequencing and live performance tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 289160.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve built recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 289160.0,
      "end_time": 292160.0,
      "text": "in which Siftables act as sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 292160.0,
      "end_time": 294160.0,
      "text": "like lead, bass and drums."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 294160.0,
      "end_time": 296160.0,
      "text": "Each of these has four different variations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 296160.0,
      "end_time": 298160.0,
      "text": "you get to choose which one you want to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 298160.0,
      "end_time": 301160.0,
      "text": "And you can inject these sounds into a sequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 304160.0,
      "text": "that you can assemble into the pattern that you want."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304160.0,
      "end_time": 308160.0,
      "text": "And you inject it by just bumping up the sound Siftable against a sequence Siftable."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 308160.0,
      "end_time": 312160.0,
      "text": "There are effects that you can control live, like reverb and filter."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 312160.0,
      "end_time": 315160.0,
      "text": "You attach it to a particular sound and then tilt to adjust it."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 315160.0,
      "end_time": 318160.0,
      "text": "And then, overall effects like tempo and volume"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 318160.0,
      "end_time": 320160.0,
      "text": "that apply to the entire sequence."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 320160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 324160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 324160.0,
      "end_time": 326160.0,
      "text": "DM: We&#39;ll start by putting a lead"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "into two sequence Siftables, arrange them into a series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 331160.0,
      "end_time": 333160.0,
      "text": "extend it, add a little more lead."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 334160.0,
      "end_time": 336160.0,
      "text": "Now I put a bass line in."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 336160.0,
      "end_time": 341160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 341160.0,
      "end_time": 343160.0,
      "text": "DM: Now I&#39;ll put some percussion in."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 343160.0,
      "end_time": 348160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 348160.0,
      "end_time": 351160.0,
      "text": "DM: And now I&#39;ll attach the filter to the drums, so I can control the effect live."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 351160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 355160.0,
      "text": "DM: I can speed up the whole sequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355160.0,
      "end_time": 358160.0,
      "text": "by tilting the tempo one way or the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358160.0,
      "end_time": 360160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 360160.0,
      "end_time": 363160.0,
      "text": "DM: And now I&#39;ll attach the filter to the bass for some more expression."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 363160.0,
      "end_time": 368160.0,
      "text": "Video: (Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 368160.0,
      "end_time": 371160.0,
      "text": "DM: I can rearrange the sequence while it plays."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 371160.0,
      "end_time": 373160.0,
      "text": "So I don&#39;t have to plan it out in advance, but I can improvise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 373160.0,
      "end_time": 375160.0,
      "text": "making it longer or shorter as I go."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 379160.0,
      "text": "And now, finally, I can fade the whole sequence out"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379160.0,
      "end_time": 382160.0,
      "text": "using the volume Siftable, tilted to the left."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 382160.0,
      "end_time": 387160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387160.0,
      "end_time": 389160.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 389160.0,
      "end_time": 392160.0,
      "text": "So, as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 392160.0,
      "end_time": 395160.0,
      "text": "my passion is for making new human-computer interfaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 395160.0,
      "end_time": 398160.0,
      "text": "that are a better match to the ways our brains and bodies work."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 398160.0,
      "end_time": 402160.0,
      "text": "And today, I had time to show you one point in this new design space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402160.0,
      "end_time": 405160.0,
      "text": "and a few of the possibilities that we&#39;re working to bring out of the laboratory."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 405160.0,
      "end_time": 407160.0,
      "text": "So the thought I want to leave you with"
